high_descs: Turn right and walk into the passage and turn right to walk down the passage and turn right to enter the bedroom and reach the sidetable.
Pick up the knife from the nightstand.
Turn around to exit the room and enter the passage and turn right to enter the kitchen to reach the lemon on the right.
Cut the slice of lemon on the left of the sink with the knife.
Turn right to exit the kitchen, turn left and head to the bedroom on the right to walk to the drawer.
Put the knife in the top drawer of the nightstand.
Turn around and turn right to exit the room and walk left down the passage and take a right turn to find the sink.
Pick up the lemon from the left sink.
Turn left to reach the microwave.
Heat the lemon slice in the microwave and take the lemon slice out.
Turn around and turn left on the passage and turn right to enter the bedroom and find the sidetable on the left.
Put the lemon slice on the sidetable.
anns.task_desc: Put the heated slice of Lemon on the SideTable.

high_descs: Turn right and walk towards the wall, then left to exit the room, then right through the hallway taking the last right into the bedroom and approaching the sidetable.
Pick up the knife from the bedstand.
Exit the room the way you came in, go left through the hallway slightly and then right into the kitchen area, stopping at the lemon.
Slice the lemon that is on the drainboard next to the sink.
Return to the drawer where you picked up the knife.
Place the knife inside the drawer of the bedstand.
Return to the sliced up lemon in the sink.
Pick up one slice of the lemon.
Walk a bit left to the microwave.
Use the microwave on the lemon, then retrieve it.
Return the sidetable where you picked up the knife.
Place the lemon slice on top of the sidetable.
anns.task_desc: Place a microwaved Lemon slice on a SideTable.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the sidetable.
Take the knife from the side table.
Then turn around and go near the lemon.
Cut the lemon into pieces using the knife.
Turn around and go to the drawer in the bedroom.
Put the knife in the drawer of the side table.
Turn around and go near the sink.
Take the piece of lemon from the sink.
Turn left and go near the microwave.
Put the lemon into the microwave oven.
Then take it out and go to the sidetable in the bedroom.
Put the lemon on the sidetable.
anns.task_desc: Placed the piece of lemon on the side table of the bedroom.
